{"tid":825642,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今日，我要創造一個代表香港嘅英雄入Marvel","createTime":"2018-09-17T16:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T12:11:55.000Z","uid":89530,"like":10,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2a74f955ab04213a01bd68235dadb6933b117cff","tid":825642,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/002557_b73171e9f33be000729e471f11cec203.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F002557_b73171e9f33be000729e471f11cec203.png&h=810fde2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n睇咗呢張相就有呢個idea<br />\n山竹吹襲香港，對香港造成災難性破壞，但亦阻擋唔住香港人返工嘅心，而領導住呢班香港人嘅英雄，就係Captain No Rest<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/003108_4f28e22a07ebdd4c6af90ed2c94488b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F003108_4f28e22a07ebdd4c6af90ed2c94488b9.png&h=3490f566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時只係一位連登巴打，但一遇到災難，就會拎起把遮成為Captain No Rest，身先士卒，第一個返工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n技能：手上嘅遮係無敵防禦，乜都擋到<br />\n其他特色想等各位一齊補完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(P.s. 無意冒犯圖中巴打，因為張相影得太中香港人今日嘅心情，苦中作樂咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"ed605deb60244707cce6593c87c498c6e349b0b2","tid":825642,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9934eb2bcdc6c45019b6d2f144072e232064e3","tid":825642,"uid":105715,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc4f7d0e53ab5bf5b6b9e9dc663355e5f8f6af6","tid":825642,"uid":199841,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:49:05.000Z","msg":"做多咗"},{"pid":"0e052cec1d32974218c7ef9b7c476d56bd6903a7","tid":825642,"uid":107733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"樓主好風趣 好想識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7b75e50efb8e9f53e2f8d159259de5d2acd7d5","tid":825642,"uid":78300,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"3.5/10"},{"pid":"1b3657ef5a0fa35195b2c5b6aea881176c7e955b","tid":825642,"uid":89530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"點解呀，個個英雄構思都要中二病先架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e3bb1ea60fa6f0da76639272bbf1449fe63643","tid":825642,"uid":152047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多"},{"pid":"afc5c710cc376247dac8422f51765c83d04ef4d1","tid":825642,"uid":10374,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"都唔知你做乜撚野"},{"pid":"3fd51866f4b70f74bc8af6420dbb977b967d2358","tid":825642,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b3657ef5a0fa35195b2c5b6aea881176c7e955b","tid":825642,"uid":89530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"點解呀，個個英雄構思都要中二病先架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"整返套衫俾佢啦"},{"pid":"b0090322caf096c583fda5a04059ff580a18474c","tid":825642,"uid":201309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70e3bb1ea60fa6f0da76639272bbf1449fe63643","tid":825642,"uid":152047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited